  it.todo("dragon-material sword, enchantment 9, damage 1000 G → payout 400 G (50% rule wins, then deductible)");

  // ---- Deductible per damage event ----
  it.todo("dragon attack damages sword (500) and amulet (300) → payout 600 G (deductible per damaged item)");

  // ---- Rounding for payout ----
  it.todo("payout calculation yielding 350.5 G → final payout 350 G (rounded down in MHPCO's favor)");

